How does it work?
How does it work? | Mälarenergi
If you want to conduct your thesis project with us, there are two ways of going about it. You can either apply for one of our advertised proposals for thesis projects, which we publish here on an ongoing basis. Since our thesis projects are based on the needs of the business, this is how we make most of the appointments.
However, you can also submit your own proposal for thesis project via the form below. You describe the area you’re interested in, and then we run this by the relevant departments or functions within the business. Naturally, we would like to take on all applicants, but unfortunately this is not possible.


